#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A haven for book lovers. <br/>Warm, inviting atmosphere with "
"knowledgeable staff. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ສະຖານທີ່ພັກຜ່ອນສຳລັບຄົນຮັກປຶ້ມ. <br/>ບັນຍາກາດທີ່ອົບອຸ່ນ, ເຊື້ອເຊີນ ພ້ອມກັບພະນັກງານທີ່ມີຄວາມຮູ້. \""

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Exceptional service and variety! <br/>They always have the perfect "
"recommendation. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການບໍລິການທີ່ດີເລີດ ແລະ ມີຄວາມຫຼາກຫຼາຍ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາມີຄຳແນະນຳທີ່ສົມບູນແບບສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their selection is outstanding. Rare finds and bestsellers all in one "
"place. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການຄັດເລືອກປຶ້ມຂອງພວກເຂົາແມ່ນໂດດເດັ່ນຫຼາຍ. ມີທັງປຶ້ມຫາຍາກ ແລະ ປຶ້ມຂາຍດີລວມຢູ່ໃນບ່ອນດຽວ. \""

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_banner
msgid ""
"\"I've never found a bookstore with such variety and charm. Every visit "
"feels like uncovering a hidden treasure!\""
msgstr ""
"\"ຂ້ອຍບໍ່ເຄີຍເຫັນຮ້ານປຶ້ມທີ່ມີຄວາມຫຼາກຫຼາຍ ແລະ ມີສະເໜ່ແບບນີ້ມາກ່ອນ. ທຸກໆຄັ້ງທີ່ມາຢ້ຽມຢາມໃຫ້ຄວາມຮູ້ສຶກຄືກັບກ"
"ານຄົ້ນພົບຊັບສົມບັດທີ່ເຊື່ອງໄວ້!\""

