#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Discover all the publications. There is probably your next favorite book amoung them."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ຄົ້ນພົບສິ່ງພິມທັງໝົດ. ອາດຈະມີປຶ້ມເຫຼັ້ມຕໍ່ໄປທີ່ທ່ານມັກລວມຢູ່ໃນນັ້ນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_image_text
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Discover the history of Belgium in this well-documented book with many illustrations and testimonials."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ຄົ້ນພົບປະຫວັດສາດຂອງປະເທດແບນຊິກໃນປຶ້ມທີ່ຮວບຮວມຂໍ້ມູນໄວ້ເປັນຢ່າງດີ ພ້ອມດ້ວຍຮູບພາບປະກອບ ແລ"
"ະ ຄຳຢືນຢັນຫຼາຍຢ່າງ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Curated collections and timeless classics, all in one place.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ຄໍເລັກຊັນທີ່ຖືກຄັດສັນມາຢ່າງດີ ແລະ ປຶ້ມຄລາສສິກຕະຫຼອດການ, ທັງໝົດລວມຢູ່ໃນບ່ອນດຽວ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_text_cover
msgid ""
"<br/>Display and manage your bookstore’s collection online with a user-"
"friendly platform that simplifies all the steps, from setup to catalog "
"management, making it easy for customers to browse and find their next "
"read.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ສະແດງ ແລະ ຈັດການຄໍເລັກຊັນຂອງຮ້ານປຶ້ມຂອງທ່ານແບບອອນໄລນ໌ ດ້ວຍແພລດຟອມທີ່ໃຊ້ງ່າຍ ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍເຮັດໃ"
"ຫ້ທຸກຂັ້ນຕອນງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໄປຈົນເຖິງການຈັດການລາຍການປຶ້ມ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສາມາດເລືອກເບິ່ງ ແລະ "
"ຊອກຫາປຶ້ມອ່ານເຫຼັ້ມຕໍ່ໄປໄດ້ຢ່າງສະດວກ.<br/>"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" "
"role=\"img\"/>  Bestselling Titles"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  ລາຍຊື່ປຶ້ມທີ່ຂາ"
"ຍດີທີ່ສຸດ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_three_columns
msgid "A Belgian Story"
msgstr "ເລື່ອງລາວຂອງແບນຊິກ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_image_title
msgid "A Deep Dive into Stories and Imagination"
msgstr "ດຳດິ່ງສູ່ໂລກແຫ່ງເລື່ອງລາວ ແລະ ຈິນຕະນາການ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_striped_center_top
msgid "A World of Knowledge Awaits"
msgstr "ໂລກແຫ່ງຄວາມຮູ້ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າທ່ານຢູ່"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A classic novel by F. Scott Fitzgerald, set in the Roaring Twenties, "
"exploring themes of wealth, love, and the American Dream."
msgstr ""
"ນິຍາຍຄລາສສິກໂດຍ F. Scott Fitzgerald, ທີ່ມີສາກໃນຍຸກປີ 1920, ສຳຫຼວດເລື່ອງລາວຂອງຄວາມຮັ່ງມີ, ຄ"
"ວາມຮັກ ແລະ ຄວາມຝັນຂອງຊາວອາເມຣິກັນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_accordion
msgid ""
"Absolutely! If a book is out of stock, you can place a special order through"
" our website or by visiting the store. We'll notify you once the book is "
"back in stock, and you can choose to pick it up in-store or have it shipped "
"to your address. Special orders typically take 1-2 weeks to fulfill, "
"depending on availability."
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ແນ່ນອນ! ຖ້າປຶ້ມໝົດສະຕັອກ, ທ່ານສາມາດສັ່ງຈອງເປັນພິເສດຜ່ານທາງເວັບໄຊ ຫຼື ເຂົ້າມາທີ່ຮ້ານ. ພວກເຮົາຈະແຈ້"
"ງໃຫ້ທ່ານຊາບເມື່ອປຶ້ມກັບມາຢູ່ໃນສະຕັອກ, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກມາຮັບຢູ່ຮ້ານ ຫຼື ໃຫ້ຈັດສົ່ງໄປຕາມທີ່ຢູ່ຂອງທ່ານ. ກ"
"ານສັ່ງຈອງພິເສດປົກກະຕິຈະໃຊ້ເວລາ 1-2 ອາທິດ, ຂຶ້ນກັບການມີຢູ່ຂອງປຶ້ມ."

